description.narrative: The Iraqi National Newborn Action Plan INAP and the National Nutrition Strategy reviewed, endorsed and implemented. Perinatal Death (PND) Auditing established in 30 MNH facilities. Updated case management of prematurity as first cause of newborn deaths developed and endorsed by counterpart. Global BFHI Guidelines adapted for Iraq and a national BFHI steering committee established. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:26/12/2018
